msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.62:0.2"
msgid "7. Saññāvagga "
msgstr "7. Perceptions "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.62:0.3"
msgid "62. Dutiyasaññāsutta "
msgstr "62. Perceptions (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.80, sc1
msgctxt "an5.62:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimā, bhikkhave, saññā bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā honti mahānisaṃsā amatogadhā amatapariyosānā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these five perceptions, when developed and cultivated, are very fruitful and beneficial. They culminate in the deathless and end with the deathless. "

msgctxt "an5.62:1.2"
msgid "Katamā pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.62:1.3"
msgid "Aniccasaññā, anattasaññā, maraṇasaññā, āhāre paṭikūlasaññā, sabbaloke anabhiratasaññā—"
msgstr "The perceptions of impermanence, not-self, death, repulsiveness of food, and dissatisfaction with the whole world. "

msgctxt "an5.62:1.4"
msgid "imā kho, bhikkhave, pañca saññā bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā honti mahānisaṃsā amatogadhā amatapariyosānā”ti. "
msgstr "These five perceptions, when developed and cultivated, are very fruitful and beneficial. They culminate in the deathless and end with the deathless.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.62:1.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

